Notes: WIAC Tournament Championship Game...UWO wins its second WIAC Tournament, with
the first being in 1999...UWO earns WIAC's automatic bid to the NCAA Div. III
Championship, its first appearance since 2000...UWO's Kuehl has 18 points and
11 rebounds...UWO scored 11 straight points to take 67-58 lead with 5:28 left.
Game.Officials: Mark Repinski,  Katie Lukanich,  Scott Doberstein
